Title: Atlantic Rhapsody - 52 myndir úr Tórshavn
Actors: Erling Eysturoy, Elin K. Mouritsen, Páll Danielsen
Plot: Presents a day in the life of a few inhabitants of Tórshavn in the Faroe Islands: A father and his daughter are having breakfast when the fire-brigade drive by. A woman and her child are looking at the fire and meet a married coup...
